## âœ… Features Implemented

### ğŸ” Authentication & Authorization
- âœ… User registration with password hashing (bcrypt)
- âœ… JWT-based authentication with HTTP-only cookies
- âœ… Secure login/logout functionality
- âœ… Role-based access control (User vs Admin)
- âœ… Protected routes with middleware

### ğŸ“ CRUD Operations (Task Entity)
- âœ… Create tasks (authenticated users)
- âœ… Read tasks (user-specific & filtered)
- âœ… Update tasks (with validation)
- âœ… Delete tasks (owner/admin only)

### ğŸ›¡ï¸ Security & Validation
- âœ… Password hashing with bcrypt (10 rounds)
- âœ… JWT token with 1-hour expiration
- âœ… HTTP-only cookies for XSS protection
- âœ… Input validation using express-validator
- âœ… Centralized error handling
- âœ… Email normalization (lowercase)

### ğŸ“š Documentation & Best Practices
- âœ… Comprehensive Postman collection
