ğŸ” Security Measures

| Feature          | Description                 |
| ---------------- | --------------------------- |
| Password Hashing | bcrypt (10 rounds)          |
| Token Security   | JWT + HTTP-only cookies     |
| Token Expiry     | 1 hour                      |
| XSS Protection   | Cookie flags & sanitization |
| Validation       | express-validator           |
| Error Handling   | Centralized middleware      |



